name: TE QUIERO From The Heat of Jakarta Sun - RHKM

metadata.description:
"TE QUIERO, From The Heat of Jakarta Sun", is a duet exhibition from Mahendra Nazar and Rukmunal Hakim, fully supported by YesGo! Ekshibisi. The exhibition also involved; Nin Djani for the exhibition foreword and text, last but not least, Karin Josephine, who built the "gallery".

Check more about the exhibition, here:  
[TE QUIERO at Sunset Limited](https://twitter.com/yesgostudio/status/1587400668351852549?s=20&t=HTU731OgX7n8n8ipEePTLA)  
[TE QUIERO at SUBO JKT](https://twitter.com/yesgostudio/status/1607363150046953473?s=20&t=HTU731OgX7n8n8ipEePTLA)
